I"Î<p>While as individuals we can work to meet these needs for ourselves, we can also supporting each other to meet these needs so that our relationships feel healthy and fulfilling.</p>

<p><strong>Authenticity</strong></p>

<p>One of our core needs is the ability to feel like we can bring our full self to our relationships.</p>

<p><strong>Connection</strong></p>

<p>We all have a need to feel like we are seen, understood and valued in our relationships.</p>
